column60: You have conquered the forest. Now you must build a kingdom worthy of your name.
In a moment of weakness the Marquise descended. Now you have rallied your strength and are poised to recapture you birthright.
You wander the woods, seeking a place in the new society that is taking shape.
The Riverfolk Company are always on the hunt for new markets. After all, where there's muck, there's clams!
For many seasons you lobbied the Ducy to invade the Woodland. Now, with the help of some powerful friendds, your time has come.
Returned from exile, you must recover relics lost in wars of old.
You're the true voice of this Woodland. Dissenters will burn.
Keep your Croco-dial locked for your soundrach to the woodland's demise
